---
title: Crisp Cauliflower Nuggets with a Spicy Bean Stew and Soured Cream
description: These crispy cauliflower ‘nuggets’ are too delicious to miss. Baked in the oven with a panko breadcrumb crust and seasoned with our delicious Central American spice, Chef Andre has really hit the mark with this delicious vegetarian recipe. Served with a spicy bean and courgette stew and topped with soured cream and fresh chopped coriander, this is a clean-plates-all-round kind of dish.
